30000k.m. ka travel  logo ki suffering ko record karney key liye
Great Barkhaji aur kuch public itna bada hadsa bhool key Hindu aur Muslim ladhai mey lagey heyn. Kia Corona virus religion dekh key attack kiatha? "Jago public Jago"
